Team Performance – Alternative gadget

Alternative to cisco’s Team Performance gadget

This sample gadget contains the following files:
TeamPerformance.css
TeamPerformance.js
TeamPerformance.xml

Usage:
1.	SFTP the gadget contents to /3rdpartygadget/root/files
2.	Edit layout xml in cfadmin to load the gadget /3rdpartygadget/files/TeamPerformance.xml
3.	Log into the agent desktop.

Advantages:
1)	LoggedOut users doesn’t displayed
2)	Agents without Supervisor role could browse own team’s persons list (without silent monitoring or state changing)
3)	If supervisor has not own team in supervised teams he can browse own team’s persons list too (without silent monitoring or state changing)
